tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE customer_service_interactions (
    interaction_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_id UUID,
    interaction_date TIMESTAMP,
    interaction_type VARCHAR(50),
    feedback TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE CustomerServiceInteractions(
  interaction_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  customer_id INT NOT NULL,
  interaction_date DATE NOT NULL,
  agent_id INT NOT NULL,
  interaction_type VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
  feedback_text TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE FeedbackAnalysis(
  feedback_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  interaction_id INT NOT NULL,
  feedback_date DATE NOT NULL,
  feedback_score INT NOT NULL,
  feedback_category VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
  feedback_details TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE interactions (
    interaction_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_id INT,
    interaction_date DATE,
    interaction_type VARCHAR(50),
    interaction_details TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE feedback (
    feedback_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    interaction_id INT,
    feedback_date DATE,
    satisfaction_rating INT,
    feedback_comments TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE customers (
    customer_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_name VARCHAR(100),
    customer_email VARCHAR(100),
    customer_phone VARCHAR(20),
    policy_number VARCHAR(20)
);

CREATE TABLE policies (
    policy_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    policy_type VARCHAR(50),
    start_date DATE,
    customer_id INT,
    FOREIGN KEY (customer_id) REFERENCES customers(customer_id)
);

CREATE TABLE interactions (
    interaction_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    interaction_date TIMESTAMP,
    customer_id INT,
    policy_id INT,
    interaction_type VARCHAR(50),
    interaction_details TEXT,
    FOREIGN KEY (customer_id) REFERENCES customers(customer_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (policy_id) REFERENCES policies(policy_id)
);

CREATE TABLE feedback (
    feedback_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    interaction_id INT,
    customer_rating INT,
    feedback_text TEXT,
    FOREIGN KEY (interaction_id) REFERENCES interactions(interaction_id)
);

CREATE TABLE CustomerServiceInteractions (
  interaction_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  customer_id INT,
  employee_id INT,
  interaction_date DATE,
  interaction_time TIME,
  interaction_details TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE Feedback (
  feedback_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  interaction_id INT,
  rating INT,
  feedback_details TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE Customers (
  customer_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  customer_name VARCHAR(50),
  policy_id INT,
  email VARCHAR(50),
  phone_number VARCHAR(15)
)

CREATE TABLE Employees (
  employee_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  employee_name VARCHAR(50),
  department VARCHAR(50),
  position VARCHAR(50),
  email VARCHAR(50)
)

CREATE TABLE Policies (
  policy_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  policy_name VARCHAR(50),
  coverage_details TEXT,
  premium_amount DECIMAL(10, 2),
  start_date DATE
)
